<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٢٢٩ - حَدَّثَنَا وَكِيعٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ أَيْمَنِ بْنِ نَابُلٍ قَالَ:</span> سَمِعْتُ طَاوُسًا،<span class="c5"> يَقُولُ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَيْسَ فِي الْمُفَصَّلِ السُّجُودُ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>